<header>
<div class='post-title'>
<h2>
<a href="the-dollars-and-sense-of-app-store-pricing">The Dollars and Sense of App Store Pricing</a>
</h2>
</div>
</header>
<div class='post-body' id='post_body_583139'>
<p>In <a target="_blank" href="http://jury.me/blog/2013/4/2/thriving-in-an-app-store-world">this excellent talk by Michael Jurewitz</a> he talks about surviving in the app store world.  The first 30 minutes are dedicated to what apple developers should do to be good apple citizens.  The second half talks about pricing your app and about avoiding the low-cost, high-quantity problem that is plaguing the app store now.</p><p><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/63161309" width="1280" height="720" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe></p>
</div>

